(174, 83, 'third_section_content', '<div class=\"title-head about-top0\">\r\n<h2 class=\"about-top0\">VISSION</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"det-text bg-screen-mrg\">\r\n\r\nWe endeavor to become an Outstanding and most Distinguished Company focused on producing the best Quality &amp; most Innovative Food Products for our Consumers. In the process, we shall build a formidable Organization that can excel and compete with the best in the Industry and ensure satisfaction &amp; fulfillment of Professional Aspirations for our Business Partners, Associates and Employees.\r\n<div class=\"text-bold\">The Spirit of Excellence is the Driving Force of the Company.</div>\r\n</div>'),
(175, 83, '_third_section_content', 'field_5d048a4583bc1'),
(176, 83, 'fourth_section_image', '36'),
(177, 83, '_fourth_section_image', 'field_5d048a9883bc2'),
(178, 83, 'fourth_section_content', '<div class=\"title-head about-top0\">\r\n<h2 class=\"about-top0\">MISSION</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"det-text bg-screen-mrg\">\r\n\r\nWe have set our primary objective to produce Healthy, Nutritious, Wholesome and Tasty Food Products for our Consumers under strict Hygienic Conditions. Our endeavor is to provide Good Food at the Right Prices ensuring Value for Money to Consumers.\r\n\r\nOur key thrust is also to make our Products available across the length and breadth of the Country. We plan to expand our portfolio from Biscuits, Cakes, Rusks to other “Ready to Eat” categories like Extruded Snacks, Ethnic Indian Snacks, Wafers and Confectionery items and thus becoming a holistic Food Company.\r\n\r\n</div>'),
(179, 83, '_fourth_section_content', 'field_5d048ab683bc3'),
