(979, 284, 'about_content', 'SAJ Food Products (P) Ltd, established in the year 2000 currently has an Annual Business Turnover of around 1100CR. it currently manufactures a spectrum of over 129 varieties of Biscuit, Cakes, Rusks, Extruded Snacks and Wafers under the BISK FARM brand. It has also launched a complete range of Ethnic Indian Snacks under a new brand called INDIAAH.\r\n\r\nBISK FARM is the Carrier Brand for SAJ Food Products, which has been developed and re-enforced into the minds of the Indian Consumers with intensive distribution along-with high amounts of inputs in Television and Print Media and other Promotional activities. Bisk Farm stands for World Class Quality, Great Taste and Innovativeness of its products.'),
