dia.</p>                               <p> Bisk Farm Just Baked is another ambitious part of the brand’s endeavour to share its goodness directly with the consumer. It showcases the Brand’s array of freshly baked Savouries, Danishes, Special Cakes, Pastries, Breads and other Confectionery items, along with a great ambience.</p>                            </div>                         </div>                      </div>                   </div>                </div>             </div>          </section>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<section class=\"bg-dark abt-normal_sec\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n               <div class=\"row\">\n                  <div class=\"abt-pres\">\n                     <div class=\"col-sm-6 pull-right\">\n                        <div class=\"div-sec clearfix\">\n                           <figure><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"http://localhost/biskfarm/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/legacy.png\"></figure>\n                        </div>\n                     </div>\n                     <div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n                        <div class=\"div-sec mob-grid clearfix\">\n                           <div class=\"title-head about-top0\">\n                              <h2 class=\"about-top0\">OUR LEGACY</h2>\n                           </div>\n                           <div class=\"det-text bg-screen-mrg\">\n                              <p>SAJ Food Products (P) Ltd, established in the year 2000 currently has an Annual Business Turnover of around 1100CR. it currently manufactures a spectrum of over 129 varieties of Biscuit, Cakes, Rusks, Extruded Snacks and Wafers under the BISK FARM brand. It has also launched a complete range of Ethnic Indian Snacks under a new brand called INDIAAH.</p>\n                              <p>BISK FARM is the Carrier Brand for SAJ Food Products, which has been developed and re-enforced into the minds of the Indian Consumers with intensive distribution along-with high amounts o